<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Pull Request Closed Notification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
        border-top: 5px solid #008c6e;
        padding: 30px 0;
      }
      .logoImage {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #008c6e;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .wrapper {
        padding: 0 20px;
      }
      .banner {
        height: 50px;
        background: #ffffff;
        color: #008c6e;
        text-align: left;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: start;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 40px;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 20px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      p {
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 25px;
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #008c6e;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        transition: background-color 0.3s;
      }
      .button:hover {
        background-color: #222e35;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
        padding: 0 20px;
      }
      .pr-details {
        background-color: #e7e7ff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      .pr-details ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        padding-left: 0;
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .pr-details li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .pr-details li:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
      .pr-details li::before {
        content: '✔ ';
        color: #008c6e;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <section class="banner">
        <h1 class="logoImage">Hikaflow</h1>
      </section>
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h1>Pull Request Closed Notification</h1>
        <p>Hi {{adminName}},</p>
        <p>
          The pull request in "{{repositoryName}}" by "{{authorName}}" has been
          closed. Here's a summary of the changes and actions taken.
        </p>
        <a href="{{reportUrl}}" class="button">Deep Analysis</a>
        <div class="pr-details">
          <p>Closure details:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Final code changes summary</li>
            <li>Resolved issues and improvements</li>
            <li>Merge status (merged or closed without merging)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p>Thank you for your contribution to maintaining code quality!</p>
        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          The Hikaflow Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email. If
          you have any questions, please contact our support team.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
